data.description: PRICE DROP! Multi-generational living. Expansive formal dining room measuring 17'x12'!! 3 bedrooms upstairs and 3 downstairs with bathrooms on both levels. Vaulted ceilings and ceiling fans. Gorgeous kitchen with Granite countertops, backsplash, stainless steel gas appliances, and more cabinet space than you'll know what to do with. 25'x20' garden (outdoor sprinkler system included). 10 year old roof. 3 miles to I-84, Columbia George Outlets, and Downtown Troutdale offering up a variety of personal services (examples: Lady Locks Salon & Spa, Gracie Technics Jiu-Jitsu), dining (Bandits Bar & Grill, Chiang Rai-Thai Cuisine), shopping and entertainment (Stark Street Theatre, Troutdale Arts Festival), coffee (Country Coffee). Neighborhood Lewellyn Park in your backyard. Nearby Historic Columbia River Hwy, Sandy River, Dabney State Park, Lewis and Clark State Park offer outdoor activities including fishing, swimming, disc golf, floating, picnics, and more.
